steps.html_instructions: Head northwest on E Grace St toward N 7th St
Take the 1st right onto N 7th St
Slight right onto the I-64 W/I-95 N/I-64 E ramp
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Interstate 64 W/Interstate 95 N/Charlottesville/Washington and merge onto I-95 N
Keep right at the fork to continue on I-64 W, follow signs for Interstate 64 W/Interstate 195 S/Powhite Pkwy/Charlottesville
Take the Interstate 81 S exit on the left toward Interstate 64 W/Lexington/Roanoke

Merge onto I-81 S
Entering Tennessee
Take exit 1B to merge onto I-40 W toward Knoxville
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-40 W, follow signs for Nashville
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-40 W, follow signs for Huntsville/Memphis/Interstate 65 S
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-40, follow signs for Memphis
Keep left to continue on I-40 W
Take exit 10B for I-40 W toward Little Rock
Exit 10B turns slightly right and becomes I-40 W

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-40 W, follow signs for Interstate 40 W/Little Rock
Entering Arkansas
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-40 W, follow signs for Little Rock
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-30 W
Take exit 139B for I-630
Continue onto I-630 W
Take exit 2B for Doctor Martin Luther King Junior Drive

Turn right onto Dr Martin Luther King Dr/M L King (signs for State Capitol Complex)
Continue to follow Dr Martin Luther King Dr
Turn left onto W 7th St
Turn right onto State Capitol
Slight right to stay on State Capitol
